=== Cultural property ===
* Bronze sutra cylinder - height 25.3 {{ill|lt=cm|Q174728|qid=Q174728|1=Centimetre}}, diameter 11.2 cm. A {{ill|lt=bronze|Q753|qid=Q753|1=Copper}} {{ill|lt=sutra container|Q11606503|qid=Q11606503|1=kyōzutsu}} from the {{ill|lt=Muromachi period|Q334845|qid=Q334845|1=Muromachi period}}. Designated as Moriyama City cultural property (craft) on August 26, {{ill|lt=1974|Q2478|qid=Q2478|1=1974}} (Showa 49).

